{
  "page": "Bryndemere Tarth",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\"><img alt=\"House Tarth.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/50px-House_Tarth.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/75px-House_Tarth.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/100px-House_Tarth.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\"><span style=\"font-size:80%;font-weight:normal\"> Lord</span><br />Bryndemere Tarth</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\"><img alt=\"House Tarth.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/50px-House_Tarth.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/75px-House_Tarth.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/c/cc/House_Tarth.svg/100px-House_Tarth.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Titles</th><td>\n<div class=\"plainlist\"><ul><li>The <a href=\"/index.php/Evenstar\" title=\"Evenstar\">Evenstar</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Evenfall\" title=\"Lord of Evenfall\">Lord of Evenfall</a></li><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Tarth\" title=\"Lord of Tarth\">Lord of Tarth</a></li></ul></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\">House Tarth</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Stormlands\" title=\"Stormlands\">Stormlander</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Bryndemere Tarth</b> was the <a href=\"/index.php/Evenstar\" title=\"Evenstar\">Evenstar</a> and the Lord of <a href=\"/index.php/Tarth\" title=\"Tarth\">Tarth</a>, and the head of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tarth\" title=\"House Tarth\">House Tarth</a> during the <a href=\"/index.php/Regency_of_Aegon_III\" title=\"Regency of Aegon III\">regency</a> of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bryndemere_Tarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>When the <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a> broke out in <a href=\"/index.php/129_AC\" title=\"129 AC\">129&#160;AC</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Otto_Hightower\" title=\"Otto Hightower\">Otto Hightower</a> suspected that the Evenstar of Tarth may side with Princess <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> It is unknown if he did or if he followed his liege lord, <a href=\"/index.php/Borros_Baratheon\" title=\"Borros Baratheon\">Borros Baratheon</a>, and supported the <a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">greens</a>.\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a>, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Gedmund_Peake\" title=\"Gedmund Peake\">Gedmund Peake</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Ned_Bean\" title=\"Ned Bean\">Ned Bean</a> were sent against <a href=\"/index.php/Racallio_Ryndoon\" title=\"Racallio Ryndoon\">Racallio Ryndoon</a>, the self-proclaimed <a href=\"/index.php/King_of_the_Narrow_Sea\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"King of the Narrow Sea\">King of the Narrow Sea</a>. On their way to the <a href=\"/index.php/Stepstones\" title=\"Stepstones\">Stepstones</a>, they were joined first by the Velaryon fleet commanded by Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Alyn_Velaryon\" title=\"Alyn Velaryon\">Alyn Velaryon</a> and then by Lord Bryndemere who brought a dozen longships to further swell their ranks. At <a href=\"/index.php/Tarth\" title=\"Tarth\">Tarth</a>, Lord Bryndemere told them Racallio had allied himself with the <a href=\"/index.php/Archon\" title=\"Archon\">Archon</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Tyrosh\" title=\"Tyrosh\">Tyrosh</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Sealord\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Sealord\">Sealord</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Bryndemere_Tarth&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, Under the Regents - War and Peace and Cattle Shows.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_blacks_and_the_greens.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i>, The Dying of the Dragons - The Blacks and the Greens.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable succession-box noprint\" style=\"margin:0.5em auto; font-size:small;clear:both;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Last known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Cameron_Tarth\" title=\"Cameron Tarth\">Cameron Tarth</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 40%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b> The <a href=\"/index.php/Evenstar\" title=\"Evenstar\">Evenstar</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Evenfall\" title=\"Lord of Evenfall\">Lord of Evenfall</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_Tarth\" title=\"Lord of Tarth\">Lord of Tarth</a> </b>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 30%; text-align: center;\" rowspan=\"1\"><b>Unknown</b><div style=\"font-size:90%\">Next known title holder:</div><b><a href=\"/index.php/Selwyn_Tarth\" title=\"Selwyn Tarth\">Selwyn Tarth</a> </b>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404114817\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.077 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.281 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 867/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 12545/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 7205/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1444/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1835/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.180/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  268.943      1 -total\n 89.67%  241.162      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 88.99%  239.332      1 Template:Infobox\n  9.70%   26.095     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.18%   11.254      4 Template:Infobox_label\n  3.43%    9.213      1 Template:S-ttl\n  2.92%    7.845      2 Template:Main_other\n  2.85%    7.655      1 Template:S-ttl/check\n  2.73%    7.329      3 Template:Ref\n  2.26%    6.084      2 Template:Date\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:25954-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404114817 and revision id 314184\n -->\n",
